            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Thanks for your work! Now (nightly after [PR#35216](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/35216)), the behavior is as follows:\n\n- The error message is gone. ✔\n- `:bn` cycles through either:\n  * listed normal buffers ✔ (excluding both unlisted normal and (listed) help-buffers\n  * help buffers (regardless if listed or unlisted) ✔\n- (the plugin mini.bracketed’s `]b` cycles through listed buffers (regardless if help or normal) independent from the original buffer)\n\nUnfortunately I cannot set this ticket to resolved bug.",
